      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JED FURY (4) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (18.02) in a Maiden at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Key player on best and worth another chance. THROWN INTO KAOS (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (18.55) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. PUSH US (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (18.38) last time in a Maiden at this track. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Must be included in calculations. ALL FOR SHOW (6) makes debut for the Kerry Schmitzer kennel. Profiles nicely and can feature in the finish.",
